data.description: The Gathering Table is an interactive cooking class that has been created for anyone who enjoys cooking, eating good food or just looking for a unique cooking experience. Our hands-on classes are designed to create a delicious family style meal focused around fresh ingredients and scratch made cooking. Our goal is to make gourmet cooking fun and easy in a kitchen that is warm and inviting. Whether you are looking to learn something new, enjoy a unique night out or celebrating a special occasion we’ve got a menu that you are sure to enjoy. We’ve created a kitchen for guests of all cooking levels and our staff is there to help you every step of the way!
